Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:05.46,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(805,215)}Blue Days / Red Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這個消息學校裡流傳的很廣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月末的學年別個人賽裡優勝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說就能和織斑同學交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這件事 一夏同學本人也知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 本人好像還不是很清楚的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像這件事是女生們之間協定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我就回自己的班級去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是啊 我也回自己的座位去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我獲得優勝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就 就和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的事情為什麼會變成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月末的學年別個人賽裡優勝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說就能織斑同學交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優勝的話就和一夏交往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該只有我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我獲得優勝了的話就沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優勝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 這次和以前不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小學四年級的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道的全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管所有人都說我無疑會取得優勝 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能參加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不戰而敗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為姐姐發表IS的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS那壓倒性的性能 因為擔心其轉化為兵器的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家人受重要人物保護計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫到處搬遷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等回過神來時 不得不與父母分開居住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終日生活在監視與竊聽之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身心俱疲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 只有劍道堅持下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我認為那是我與一夏唯一的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但時那一天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醜陋無比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍法就如同自身的鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的劍道 僅僅只是是為了擊倒對方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發洩怨氣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是單純的暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本算不上強大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強大指的並不是這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不再迷失「強大」的真意取得勝利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一定要獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手不是別人 正是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為我是第一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正以學年別個人賽的優勝為目標而進行特訓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是完全一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這次機會 到底誰更強 在這裡分個高下也不壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰更加強大優雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡跟你做個了斷好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更強是顯而易見的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說的越弱的狗吠的越凶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來所言不假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己更強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意大聲說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些地方都很典型嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原原本本還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國第三世代機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}Schwarzer regen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞拉·布迪威伊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上來就打過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽子不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中國的甲龍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和英國的藍色之淚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看數據的時候感覺還有點強的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 要幹一場麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大老遠從德國跑過來討打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是有夠M的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你們的土豆農場裡流行這套玩意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀鈴同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的那位好像和我們沒什麼共同語言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太欺負人家就太可憐了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你們這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然和我一樣都是第三世代的專用機持有者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了人多沒有其他長處的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和只能倚老賣老的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來還真是人才不足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人希望變成殘疾的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倆還是一起上如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我還怕輸給你們這種為了只下種馬就爭的不可開交的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像只聽見說 請盡情的痛毆我吧 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連不在場的人都去侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來需要好好管教一下你那張賤嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 今天也去特訓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離比賽的日子沒幾天了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是第三競技場三個代表候補生在進行模擬戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凰同學和 奧盧卡多同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞拉·布迪威伊也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的黑色之雨的停止結界面前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍咆被停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Ａ．Ｉ．Ｃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝備了那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不需要閃躲龍咆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ａ．Ｉ．Ｃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色之雨的第三世代型兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Active inertial canceller
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也叫慣性停止能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到被克成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的成品也好意思說是第三世代機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑之極
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種狀況還想使用有延遲的空間壓縮武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼近的距離發射導彈 你還真是亂來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱怨待會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣無疑就能造成傷害…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們的防護罩能量會撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果傷害持續累積
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS機體強制解除的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼她們兩人的生命就有危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 勞拉 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情用事的直線突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典型的蠢貨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我和黑色之雨面前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是無數凡人中的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 趕緊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 雜魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了白式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再使用一次瞬間加速！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看到了狼狽的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都還有意識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有專用機的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能在這裡看著而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你見識一下世代差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說帶小孩麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千冬姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進行模擬戰是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練競技場的隔離板都遭到破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為教師 我就不能當做沒看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥的勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就留到學年戰的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然教官您這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑 德諾阿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個也沒有異議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對教師要用「是」來回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也認為那樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到學年戰開始為止 禁止一切私鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你不來救我們也沒關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣繼續下去的話都已經贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位都不要逞強啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逞強？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位都是因為被喜歡的人看到了自己落魄的一面而不好意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什什什什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我才沒有逞強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你們為什麼會和勞拉對戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性的尊嚴被侮辱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難道是說起一夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是多嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是啊 太多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個明明都是傷患
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 果然還痛不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋呢 都說了不要逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我笨蛋是什麼意思啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏才是大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月進行的學年別比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了進行更真實的模擬戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須雙人一組參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 沒能組隊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會由抽籤來決定組隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截止日期是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 和我一組吧 斑織同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我配對吧 德諾阿君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和查理一組 所以你們放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起和其他女生配組的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生一組的話儼然一幅畫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 和我配組啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是青梅竹馬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 作為同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該和我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位的IS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受損程度已經超過了C級
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓你們參加比賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣？ 我完全可以戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短期內不專心於修復的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日後會引發嚴重的結果哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得優勝的話她也可以和一夏交往了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那個一定要阻止才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來的話…獲得優勝的就該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 你們兩個 一定要獲得優勝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要連我們的份一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打從心底為你們加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 為了能回報你們這份心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美好的友情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 雖然晚了點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過謝謝你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我有做過什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 在保健室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要和我組隊參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和別的什麼人組隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的身份暴露了的話會很麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏真溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  只有我在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強自己用男生口吻說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在來這裡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不暴露身份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被強迫徹底地記住了男生的動作表情和用語
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難立刻改過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 如果一夏在意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們兩人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力像女孩子那樣說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得男生口吻的查理也很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是騙我的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有騙你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那就先換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起 我去外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不用啦 這樣對你太不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我並不在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 即便你這麼說 我還是會在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是都是男生 換衣服的時候還要去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會讓人覺得很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我們背對背換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳被纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能尖叫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出來 一夏還喜歡來硬的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好和我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也無所謂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是睡吧 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次覺得自己被別人所需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這還真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級的話是選拔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年級的話是一年來成果的檢驗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自對應的人都已經來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帚是和誰配組呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能確定配組的 說是由抽籤來決定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏同學好像只在意和布迪威伊同學的對戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別衝動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布迪威伊同學恐怕是一年級中現在最強的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰對手確定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼組合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於開始了呢 命運之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是別去特色的雙人對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅在觀眾席看著都好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.26,0:23:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是四個人都是同班…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~ 支持哪邊好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我支持斑織同學那組
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我支持德諾阿同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都是同一組的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 FIND OUT MY MIND
